	<introduction id="introduction" obligation="informative"><title>Introduction</title><clause id="_purpose_and_scope" obligation="informative"><title>Purpose and Scope</title><p id="_c6079798-aa28-4f12-a925-f75a54e91ffe">The purpose of this document is to provide guidance to mariners to help them collect and contribute
